          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Even if you have full replacement coverage for your car, having it stolen can upend your life. It’s understandable why more people are fighting back in the face of little help from law enforcement which is stretched thin after getting funding slashed as a fashion statement. One recent example of how one man was able to thwart thieves comes out of Toronto thanks to Apple AirTags.",
